data.title: 853 Mason Ave, Aurora, IL 60506
data.meta_description: Zillow has 27 photos of this $199,900 3 beds, 1 bath, 2,576 Square Feet single family home located at 853 Mason Ave, Aurora, IL 60506 MLS #12067004.
data.text: If you are a nature lover, this one is for you - This 3 bedroom, 1 bath ranch home faces the South River Street Park and the Fox River. This home is an AS-IS estate sale that is available for immediate possession. The home offers a wonderful front deck and upon entering the home, you will find a comfortable enclosed porch waiting for you. The home boasts a sitting area for reading and a lovely combo living and dining area. The kitchen is large enough for a table and chairs. Basement is waiting for your design. Although this is an AS-IS home bring your handyman or contractor to customize and personalize your personal touch. Mature tree in rear fenced backyard will give you plenty of shade and is great for entertainment. The extended driveway is ample for 3 or 4 parking space. Rather fishing, nature strolls, or seeking peace - you are a walk to the park/playground and the Fox River bike/walking trail. This one is waiting on you.
